      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 133,
      "message": "I agree, but this name needs to match between several components including dcae-bootstrap, policy-handler, etc., and {{ include \"common.name\" . }} would resolve to different values in each component I thought.  To cause the least turmoil, I hard-coded the previous resolved value.",
